Irin wannan yanayin na karamin matsin lamba a Arizona ba shi da yawa, amma, a farkon mako mai zuwa, wannan shine ainihin abin da zai faru yayin da ragowar ƙarfin Rosa ke motsawa zuwa hamada ta kudu maso yamma, yana haifar da yanayin ambaliyar ruwa.
