"Tun daga shekara ta 1950, a cikin mil 200 na birnin Phoenix, aƙalla guguwa goma ne kawai suka kawo hadari ko kuma matsin lamba!
"Guguwar Katrina (1967) ta kasance mai ƙarfi a cikin mil 40 na iyakar AES", in ji National Weather Service a Phoenix.
Sabbin samfuran Cibiyar Hurricane ta Kasa sun yi hasashen ruwan sama na 2 zuwa 4 inci, tare da yiwuwar samun ruwan sama na insulation har zuwa 5 inci a Mogollon Rim na Arizona.
