Kanye West: Mai rap din ya kira sunansa "Joe"
Wani mawaki mai suna Kanye West ya sauya sunansa zuwa "Y".
A ranar Asabar, ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "Wanda ake kira Kanye West".
'Y' ya kasance mai suna biyu ga West mai shekaru arba'in da ɗaya, kuma ya yi amfani da wannan sunan a matsayin sunan kundin wakarsa na takwas wanda ya fito a watan Yuni.
Za a sake masa suna a ranar Asabar da dare, kuma ana sa ran zai fitar da sabon album dinsa na Yandy.
Mahaliccin wasan kwaikwayon ya ce West zai maye gurbin Ariana Grande, wacce ta fice daga wasan kwaikwayon saboda 'dalilai na motsin rai'.
West ya ce sunan ba wai kawai gajerar sunan sana'a ba ne, amma kuma yana da ma'anar addini.
"Na yi imani cewa kalmar da aka fi amfani da ita a cikin Littafi Mai Tsarki ita ce 'Y' kuma 'Y' na nufin 'ku,'" in ji West a farkon wannan shekarar, yayin da yake tattauna taken kundin waƙarsa da Big Boy.
"Saboda haka, ni ne ku, ni ne mu, duk mu ne.
Na tafi daga kan'ya, wanda ke nufin ɗaya, zuwa ku - ko da kuwa abin da muke da kyau ko mara kyau ko rikicewa, wannan shine abin da muke nunawa.
Wannan kundin yana nuna ko wanene mu".
West yana cikin shahararrun masu canja sunayen masu rap.
Sean Combs, wanda aka fi sani da sunayen daban-daban kamar su Puff Daddy, P Daddy ko Daddy, ya ce sunayen da ya fi so a wannan shekara sune Love da Brother Love.
Wani dan rapper mai suna Jay-S, wanda ya yi aiki da West, ya canza sunansa zuwa "Ba tare da hyphens da manyan haruffa ba".
Shugaban kasar Mexico ya ce ba za a yi amfani da dakarun soji ba wajen kashe fararen hula
A lokacin da kasar ke gab da cika shekaru 50 da kisan gilla da aka yi wa daliban, sabon shugaban kasar Mexico, Andreas Manuel Lopez Obrador, ya ce ba za a taba amfani da karfin soja kan talakawa ba.
A Tlatelolco Plaza, Lopez Obrador ya ce "ba za a taba amfani da sojoji ba wajen zaluntar mutanen Mexico".
A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, sojojin sun kai hari a kan wani zanga-zanga da aka yi a Plaza, inda aka kashe mutane kusan 300. Wannan ya faru ne a lokacin da ƙungiyoyin ɗalibai na hagu suka soma tasowa a Latin Amirka.
Lopez Obrador ya kuma yi alkawarin tallafawa matasa na Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin kowane wata ga ɗaliban da ke karatu da buɗe ƙarin jami'o'in jama'a.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin damar ilimi ne ke sa matasa shiga cikin ƙungiyoyin masu laifi.
Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa don bunkasa ilimin kere kere
Kai-Fu Lee, wani mai saka jari kuma mai aikin AI, wanda ya yi aiki a Google, Microsoft da Apple, ya bukaci Amurka ta ninka yawan kudaden da take kashewa kan bincike a fannin, yayin da kasar Sin ke kara shiga cikin fasahar kere kere.
Kai-Fuli ya yi wannan furucin ne bayan da aka yi sanarwar AI ta bangarori daban-daban na gwamnatin Amurka, duk da cewa Amurka ba ta da wata manufa ta AI.
A shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta gabatar da wani shiri da nufin kasancewa a kan gaba wajen kirkirar abubuwa a duniya nan da shekarar 2030.
"Ganin cewa sauran ƙasashe suna baya da Amurka, ninka kasafin kuɗin bincike na AI zai zama kyakkyawan farawa, kuma muna sa ido kan ci gaban gaba a AI", in ji Lee.
A wata hira da ya yi da CNBC a wannan makon, Lee ya ce, ninka tallafin yana nufin cewa babbar nasarar AI na gaba za ta kasance a Amurka.
Lee, wanda ya rubuta littafin da Huffton Mifflin Harcourt ya wallafa mai taken "AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order", yanzu shine Shugaba na Sinovation Ventures, kuma Lee ya saka hannun jari a cikin babbar kamfanin AI na kasar Sin, Face ++.
A shekarar 1980 a Carnegie Mellon University, ya gina wani tsarin AI, wanda ya doke dan wasan Othello na Amurka mafi girma, kuma daga bisani ya zama mai zartarwa a Microsoft Research da kuma shugaban kamfanin Google na kasar Sin.
Lee ya yaba da tasirin gasar fasahar gwamnatin Amurka kamar Robotics Challenge na Hukumar Binciken Ci Gaban Tsaro, kuma ya tambaya lokacin da za a sami damar saduwa da masu falsafa na gaba.
Lee ya ce masu bincike a Amurka sukan sha wahala sosai wajen neman tallafin gwamnati.
"Shugabannin kamfanoni ne suke daukar manyan jami'ai daga China", in ji Lee.
Facebook, Google da sauran kamfanonin fasaha sun yi amfani da manyan jami'o'i don yin aiki a kan AI a cikin 'yan shekarun nan.
Lee ya ce sauye-sauyen manufofin shige da fice na iya taimakawa wajen tallafawa kokarin da Amurka ke yi na AI.
"Ina ganin dole ne a ba wa masu neman digirin digirgir a fannin AI, takardar izinin shiga kasar", in ji Lee.
A watan Yulin 2017, Majalisar Jiha ta kasar Sin ta fitar da shirin bunkasa fasahar kere kere na gaba.
Kamar yadda National Science Foundation da sauran hukumomin gwamnati ke tallafawa masu binciken Amurka, haka ma National Natural Science Foundation na kasar Sin na tallafawa mutane a cibiyoyin ilimi, amma jami'an kimiyya a kasar Sin ba su da inganci.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Ma'aikatar Tsaro ta Amurka ta kafa Cibiyar Haɗin Kai ta Artificial Intelligence, wanda ke da niyyar haɗa masu ruwa da tsaki daga masana'antu da kuma ilimin kimiyya, kuma fadar White House ta sanar da kafa wani zaɓaɓɓen kwamiti kan batun.
A wannan watan, DAPRA ta sanar da cewa za ta zuba dala biliyan biyu a wani shiri mai suna AI Next.
Idan muka duba NSF, tana zuba jari sama da dala miliyan 100 a shekara a binciken AI.
A halin yanzu, babu wani mataki da aka dauka a kan dokar Amurka da ta bukaci kafa kwamitin tsaro na kasa kan batun kere kere na wucin gadi, tsawon watanni.
