Ibrocks na neman samun nasarar farko a waje tun bayan nasara 4-1 a St. Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma Gary Holt ya ci karo da kashi na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin manajan Gerard, wanda ya sa ya ci gaba da zama maki takwas a baya da Hearts, wanda ya ci gaba da zama babban dan wasan gasar.
Menga ya ci kwallo da minti bakwai kafin a tashi daga raga, amma ba a ganin yadda za a yi a wasan da 'yan Rangers suka yi.
Rangers sun koma matsayi na shida, Livingston ya koma uku, sai dai a baya da Hibernian.
Layin da aka jefa daga baya a kan kansa da kuma Layin Layin da aka jefa daga baya zai iya sa Rangers su yi wahala.
Gerard ya yi sau takwas a tawagar da ta kai wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin duniya ta Bedford bayan da ya yi wa Irr a baya.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya yi amfani da wannan Livy 11 da ya ci Hart a makon da ya gabata, kuma wannan rukunin da suka yi horo sosai ya sa abokan hamayyarsa farin ciki a kowane mataki.
Duk da cewa Rangers sun mamaye matsayin, Livingston ya yi amfani da kwallon da suka samu.
Ya kamata su ci kwallo a minti na biyu na wasan, lokacin da aka tura Mengo ta farko a raga, Scott Pittman, zuwa ga Allen McGregor, amma dan wasan ya ɓata babbar damarsa.
Ko da yake wani ɗan iska mai ƙwarewa na Kagan Jacobs ya kusanci Kyaftin Craig Halkett, abokin aikinsa Alan Lithgow ya sami damar buga harbi mai ƙarfi zuwa bayan gidan.
Duk da cewa Rangers sun ci gaba da taka leda, an ga cewa suna da bege fiye da imani.
A minti na 15 da aka yi wa Alfredo Morelos da Steven Lawless, ya yi tunanin cewa ya kamata a yi masa bugun jini, amma alƙali Steven Thompson ya ƙi roƙon dan wasan.
Sai dai an yi harbi biyu a wasan a farkon rabin, amma wani ciwon kai da Lassanne Colibaly ya yi da kuma wani ciwo da Ovie Izaria ya yi bai dame tsohon mai tsaron raga na Iberox ba, Liam Kelly.
Ko da yake kwallo na minti 34 na Livi ya saɓa wa yanayin wasan, amma idan aka yi la'akari da haɗin kansu, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan.
Ranger sun sake kasawa wajen sarrafa wani saitin da Jacobs ya fi kowa iyawa.
Scott Orfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba Scott Robinson kwallon. Robinson ya zaɓi Mangan don kammala mai sauƙi ba tare da ya ba da kwanciyar hankali ba.
Gerard ya amsa da sauke Ryan Kent a maimakon Kolibaly a lokacin hutu. Canjin ya kasance kusan ba zato ba tsammani.
Amma Livingston ya sa 'yan wasan su yi wasa da kyau, Lithgow da Halkett sun yi dogon harbi a jere.
Holt zai iya jan ragamarsa a ƙarshen zagaye, amma McGregor ya hana Jacobs da Lithgow damar.
Mai maye gurbin Rangers, Glenn Middleton ya yi jayayya game da wani jinkirin fansa lokacin da ya haɗu da Jacobs, amma Thompson ya sake ƙin shi.
Mai bincike: wanda ya kirkiro Geiger counter
Yanzu shafi daga jaridarmu ta "Sun Day Morning": 30 ga Satumba, 1882, shekara 136 da ta gabata, a ranar da aka haifi Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger, masanin kimiyyar lissafi a Jamus.
Geiger ya haɓaka hanyar ganowa da auna ayyukan rediyo, wanda shine ƙirƙirar da ya haifar da kayan aikin da aka sani da Geiger counter.
Tun daga wannan lokacin, Geiger Counter ya zama babban abin tunani a fannin kimiyya da al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda aka gani a fim din "Bells of Coronado" wanda aka buga a 1950, wanda ya hada da Roy Rogers da Dale Evans a matsayin masanan kimiyya:
Mutum: "Mene ne wannan makirci?"
Rogers: "Wannan shi ne Geiger counter da ake amfani da shi wajen gano ma'adanai masu aikin rediyo kamar uranium.
Idan ka kunna waɗannan na'urorin, za ka iya jin tasirin da atom ɗin ke yi a cikin ma'adanai".
Evans: "Ka gaya mini, na tabbata cewa yana fashewa yanzu!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a 1945, 'yan kwanaki bayan ranar haihuwarsa ta 63.
Amma har yanzu yana da suna, kuma ya kasance a cikin wannan binciken.
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar kansa za ta koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikinmu gano ƙwayoyin cuta.
Sabuwar allurar rigakafin cutar za ta iya koyar da tsarin garkuwar jikin mutum wajen ganowa da kuma kashe ƙwayoyin daji.
Rigakafin ya koya wa tsarin garkuwar jikin mutum gane kwayoyin cuta a matsayin wani ɓangare na magani.
Wannan tsari na daukar kwayoyin cuta daga jikin mai cutar kuma a gyara su a dakin gwaje-gwaje.
Bayan haka, za su iya ganin furotin da ke haifar da wasu cututtuka, kuma su sake saka waɗannan ƙwayoyin cikin marasa lafiya.
Wani gwaji na rigakafi a kan marasa lafiya da ke fama da cututtukan daji da dama yana nuna kyakkyawan sakamako.
Lokacin da aka yi wa wata mata magani da maganin rigakafi wanda ke koyar da tsarin rigakafinta wajen gano ƙwayoyin cuta, cutar kansa ta ƙwanƙwasa ta ɓace fiye da watanni 18.
Wannan tsari ya ƙunshi cire ƙwayoyin cuta daga mai haƙuri da kuma canza su a cikin dakin gwaje-gwaje don su iya "ganin" wani furotin na kowa wanda ake kira HER2, wanda ke haifar da yawancin cututtukan daji, sannan a sake yin allurar waɗannan ƙwayoyin cikin mai haƙuri.
"Sakamakonmu ya nuna cewa muna da riga-kafi mai kyau", in ji Farfesa Jay Bersofsky na Cibiyar Kula da Ciwon Ciwon Cutar Amirka a Bethesda, Maryland.
Farfesa Bersofsky ya bayyana cewa HER2 yana shafar ci gaban nau'ikan cututtukan daji da yawa, ciki har da ciwon nono, ciwon daji na ovarian, ciwon huhu, da ciwon daji na hanji.
Irin wannan tsarin da ake amfani da shi wajen cire kwayoyin cuta daga cikin marasa lafiya da kuma koya musu yadda za su kai wa kwayoyin cutar kansa hari, ya yi nasara wajen magance cutar sankarar bargo.
