China ta ba da rahoton karuwar 14% na sabbin cututtukan HIV/AIDS
Kasar Sin ta ce yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS ya karu da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya sun ce sama da mutane 820,000 ne suka kamu da cutar a kasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018, an sami sabbin mutane kusan 40,000.
Yawancin sabbin shari'o'in suna yadawa ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ke nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar amfani da jini daga mutane masu kamuwa da cutar, wanda aka yi amfani da shi wajen canza jini.
Amma, jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce a wani taro a lardin Yunnan, an kusan kawar da yawan masu dauke da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar.
Duk da haka, adadin masu kamuwa da cutar HIV da cutar kanjamau a kasar Sin na karuwa da kusan miliyan daya a kowace shekara.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i tsakanin al'ummomin LGBT na kasar Sin babbar matsala ce.
Kasar Sin ta yi wa luwadi yankan-kasar a shekarar 1997, duk da haka, nuna bambanci ga mutanen LGBT ya ci gaba da kasancewa mai tsanani.
Saboda dabi'u masu ra'ayin mazan jiya a kasar, binciken ya nuna cewa kashi 70-90% na mazajen da ke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure da matan.
Sau da yawa ana samun cututtuka ne domin maza ba sa samun isasshen kariya ta jima'i sa'ad da suke yin jima'i da juna.
A wani bangare na kokarin magance wannan matsalar, tun daga shekarar 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samar da magungunan cutar HIV a ko'ina.
