Menene bikin Global Citizen, kuma ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, New York za ta karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wanda zai kasance da wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na shekara-shekara, da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa: kawar da talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, dubun dubatan mutane sun yi ta tururuwa zuwa Babban Gidan Lawn na Central Park don halartar bikin Global Citizen Festival ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B, da Shawn Mendes ba, amma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin taron na kawar da matsanancin talauci ta 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka fara a shekarar 2012, wani fadada ne na Global Prosperity Project, wata kungiya ta kasa da kasa da ke aiki don kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan masu fafutukar yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don halartar taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikitin VIP), masoya na kide kide dole ne suyi ayyuka da yawa ko "ayyuka"; waɗannan ayyukan sun haɗa da ba da gudummawa, imel, kiran waya ga shugaban duniya, da sauran hanyoyi masu ma'ana waɗanda zasu taimaka haɓaka wayar da kan jama'a game da burinsu na kawar da talauci.
Amma da yake muna da shekaru 12 da isa ga wannan, yaya Global Citizen ya yi nasara?
Shin bayar da tikitin kyauta ne hanya ta musamman da za a sa mutane su amsa kira zuwa ga aiki ko kuwa wani nau'i ne na abin da ake kira "kikinci" - sa hannu a gunaguni ko aika tweet - wani nau'i ne na rashin amfani da jama'a da suke ganin suna kawo canji ta hanyar yin hakan?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ta ce ta rubuta sama da "matakai" miliyan 19 daga masu goyon baya, don taimakawa dandamali na manufofi daban-daban.
Ya ce, wadannan matakan sun taimaka wajen tura shugabannin duniya su sanar da kudaden da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da kuma manufofi da nufin sauya rayuwar mutane biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, rukunin ya zaɓi alkawura da sanarwa 390 da suka samo asali daga ayyukansa, kuma ya ba da gudummawa ko kuma tara kuɗi na kusan dala biliyan 10.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da suka tara sun shafi mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Daya daga cikin muhimman alkawuran shine cewa bayan karbar sama da tweets 4,700 daga Global Citizens, an yi musu alkawarin $35m don taimakawa kasar ta kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a Rwanda.
Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa, da 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihi, in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan Power of Nutrition, a wani taron kide kide da wake a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Bayan da aka dauki matakai sama da 5,000, inda aka yi kira ga Burtaniya da ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara, gwamnati ta sanar da cewa za ta ba da tallafin kuɗi ga shirin Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 cikin abinci mai gina jiki.
Tambayar da ake yawan yi a shafinta ita ce, "Me ya sa kuke ganin za ku iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ta amsa: "Zai kasance hanya mai tsawo da wahala - wani lokacin za mu yi tuntuɓe kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar yadda muke da babbar motsi na 'yancin jama'a da na nuna bambanci, za mu yi nasara, domin tare muna da ƙarfi.
A wannan shekara, Janet Jackson, Weekend, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, da Janelle Moni za su yi wasan kwaikwayo a taron da ke faruwa a New York, kuma Deborah-Lee Furness da Huff Jackman za su shirya shi.
