A yakin cinikayya, China ta riga ta kara yawan harajin da take sakawa Amurka, kuma wani masanin tattalin arziki a China da Amurka ya ce an tsara sabon harajin ne don yin niyya ga kamfanonin shigo da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican.
