Dali, wanda ya lashe lambar tagulla sau biyu a wasannin Olympics, yanzu ya zama babban mai ba da shawara na LGBT, kuma ya yi amfani da kasancewarsa a wasannin Commonwealth da aka yi a Ostiraliya a wannan shekara don yin kira ga ƙarin ƙasashe don halatta bambancin jinsi.
