An sake jinkirta fara aiki da sabon jirgin ruwan yaki na Jamus.
Sabon jirgin ruwan yakin Jamus wanda ya maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwan da aka yi amfani da su a lokacin Cold War ya kamata a fara aiki a shekarar 2014, amma ba za a fara aiki ba har sai a kalla shekara mai zuwa saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma tsadar snowballing, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
Jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito wani mai magana da yawun sojin cewa, an dage ƙaddamar da Rhineland-Falce, babban jirgin ruwan sabon jirgin Baden-Württemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
An shirya cewa Sojan Ruwa zai karbi jirgin a shekarar 2014, amma matsalar da aka fuskanta kafin isar da jirgin ta yi tasiri a kan aikin.
A shekarar 2007, rundunar sojin ta bada umarnin samar da jiragen ruwa guda hudu na Baden-Württemberg, domin maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An san cewa jiragen ruwa suna da manyan makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da wasu fasahohi na sirri kamar radar, infrared, da siginar sauti.
